cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for document classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of embeddings, which are commonly used in machine learning and deep learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also deals with optimization and efficiency, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper mentions experiments with image classification, which could also fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
